{"word":"G4066 - περίχωρος - períchōros - per-ikh'-o-ros - Country about","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περίχωρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">períchōros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">per-ikh'-o-ros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Country about</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சுற்றுப்புற, சுற்றிலுமுள்ள, சுற்றியிருக்கிற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"lying around about, neighboring"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G5561 - χώρα - chṓra - kho'-rah/5561\">G5561</a>; <i>around</i> the <i>region</i>, that is, <i>circumjacent</i> (as noun, with <a href=\"#/G1093 - γῆ - gē - ghay/1093\">G1093</a> implied, <i>vicinity</i>): - country (round) about, region (that lieth) round about.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}